import React from 'react';
import {Button, Form} from '@mui/material';

export default function form() {
  return (

      <Form>
          <label>Nome:
              <input type="text" />
          </label>

          <label>Sobrenome:
              <input type="text" />
          </label>

          <label>CPF:
              <input type="text" />
          </label>

          <label>Promocoes:
              <input type="text" />
          </label>

          <label>Novidades:
              <input type="checkbox" />
          </label>

          <Button type="submit" variant="contained" >Cadastrar</Button>
      </Form>
  )
}
